Clare Greet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clare_Greet 0 Clare Greet (14 June 1871 – 14 February 1939) was an English stage and film actress. She appeared in 26 films between 1921 and 1939, including seven films directed by (and one produced by) Alfred Hitchcock. She was born in Leicestershire and died in London.
